0.Details URL
https://qiita.com/emurin/items/f9c2ebd773a9d5b18308

1.Download jar files
Selenium Standalone Server:3.14.0
Google Chrome Driver:2.41

2.Setup chrome browser IDE
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/selenium-ide/mooikfkahbdckldjjndioackbalphokd

3.Start up Selenium remote hub and node
#Start hub
java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=chromedriver.exe -jar selenium-server-standalone-3.14.0.jar -role hub
#Start node
java -Dwebdriver.chrome.driver=chromedriver.exe -jar selenium-server-standalone-3.14.0.jar -role node
